Go implementation of Balloon memory-hard hash (https://crypto.stanford.edu/balloon/)
created by Dan Boneh, Henry Corrigan-Gibbs and Stuart Schechter.

DOCUMENTATION

    https://godoc.org/github.com/nogoegst/balloon

